manifests.contents:
[workspace]
members = ["bin/*", "crates/*", "contracts/*"]
resolver = "2"

[workspace.dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1"
eyre = "0.6"
futures = "0.3"
hex = "0.4"
log = "0.4"
near-crypto = "0.17.0"
near-jsonrpc-client = "0.6.0"
near-jsonrpc-primitives = "0.17.0"
near-primitives = "0.17.0"
near-sdk = "4.0.0"
near-sdk-contract-tools = "1.0.1"
rand = "0.8"
serde_json = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"

[workspace.dependencies.borsh]
version = "0.10.3"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.serde_with]
version = "3.4"
features = ["hex", "base64", "macros"]
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["env-filter"]

[workspace.package]
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Pagoda <hello@near.org>"]

[profile.release]
opt-level = "z"
debug = false
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"
overflow-checks = true

[profile.release.package]

bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "near-da-http-api"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[package]
name = "near-da-http-api"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.version]
workspace = true

[package.authors]
workspace = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.75"
axum = "0.6"
serde = "1"
serde_json = "1.0.108"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.4"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.hex]
workspace = true

[dependencies.near-da-http-api-data]
path = "../../crates/http-api-data"

[dependencies.near-da-primitives]
path = "../../crates/primitives"

[dependencies.near-da-rpc]
path = "../../crates/da-rpc"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.4"
features = ["trace"]

[dependencies.tracing]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
workspace = true

bin = []
bench = []
example = []

[[test]]

name = "tests"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[package]
name = "near-da-blob-store"

autotests = true
autobenches = true

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.version]
workspace = true

[package.authors]
workspace = true

[dependencies.borsh]
workspace = true

[dependencies.near-sdk]
workspace = true

[dependencies.uint]

[dev-dependencies]
